title: [Candy Apple Shoppe, Backroom]
description: This exceptionally small room is stacked high with small, wooden slat-walled baskets, some stained and others pristine, obviously meant to be used for picking apples and other bounties found within the orchard.  A small sign hangs above a narrow opening on the wall between two stacks.
